public class ExpressionPanel
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Composite

Expression toolbar to be displayed when expression analysis is successfully carried out. Renders the Radio Button Group for user to select the time of the expression and the expression scale for the user to map the color value back to the expression level
